rincipal que ejecuta acciones en un sistema o aplicación.\"\n    }\n  }\n],\n    \"imageUrl\": \"link\",\n    \"backgroundColor\": \"#FFF3E0\",\n    \"audioUrl\": \"link\",\n    \"avatar\": {\n      \"name\": \"Lina\",\n      \"imageUrl\": \"link\",\n      \"position\": \"bottomLeft\"\n    }\n  }" },// code snippet
                                        new LessonContentDTO { Id = 1003, LessonId = 1001, TypeId = 2, Order = 3, Content = " {\n     \"title\": {\n      \"en\": \"Match de tecnologías de Angular\",\n      \"es\": \"Angular Technologies Match\"\n    },\n    \"exercise\": [\n      {\n        \"type\": \"match\",\n        \"completed\": false,\n        \"instruction\": {\n          \"en\": \"Match each concept on the left to its correct description on the right.\",\n          \"es\": \"Arrastra cada concepto de la izquierda hacia su descripción correcta en la derecha.\"\n        },\n        \"left\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"framework\",\n            \"text\": \"Framework\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"component\",\n            \"text\": \"Component\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"html\",\n            \"text\": \"HTML\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"css\",\n            \"text\": \"CSS\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"ts\",\n            \"text\": \"TS\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"right\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"desc_framework\",\n            \"text\": \"A structure/base used to build web applications.\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"desc_component\",\n            \"text\": \"A reusable part of the interface made of HTML, CSS, and TS.\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"desc_html\",\n            \"text\": \"Defines the structure and layout of the web page.\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"desc_css\",\n            \"text\": \"Adds visual styles like colors and spacing to HTML.\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"desc_ts\",\n            \"text\": \"Contains the logic of the component.\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"pairs\": [\n          {\n            \"left\": \"framework\",\n            \"right\": \"desc_framework\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"left\": \"component\",\n            \"right\": \"desc_component\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"left\": \"html\",\n            \"right\": \"desc_html\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"left\": \"css\",\n            \"right\": \"desc_css\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"left\": \"ts\",\n            \"right\": \"desc_ts\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"imageUrl\": \"link\",\n    \"backgroundColor\": \"#FFF3E0\",\n    \"audioUrl\": \"link\",\n    \"avatar\": {\n      \"name\": \"Lina\",\n      \"imageUrl\": \"link\",\n      \"position\": \"bottomLeft\"\n    }\n  }" },// code snippet
                                        new LessonContentDTO { Id = 1004, LessonId = 1001, TypeId = 2 ,Order = 4, Content = " {\n    \"title\": {\n      \"en\": \"Angular Technologies\",\n      \"es\": \"Tecnologías de Angular\"\n    },\n    \"exercise\": [\n      {\n        \"type\": \"options\",\n        \"completed\": false,\n        \"instruction\": {\n          \"en\": \"Based on the previous analogy, the engine refers to which technology?\",\n          \"es\": \"Según la analogía vista anteriormente. El motor, ¿A qué tecnología hace referencia?\"\n        },\n        \"options\": [\n          {\n            \"text\": \"Node\",\n            \"correct\": true,\n            \"output\": {\n              \"en\": \"JavaScript runtime environment. Correct!\",\n              \"es\": \"El entorno de ejecución de JavaScript. Correcto.\"\n            }\n          },\n          {\n            \"text\": \"npm\",\n            \"correct\": false,\n            \"output\": {\n              \"en\": \"npm is the package manager, not the engine.\",\n              \"es\": \"npm es el gestor de paquetes, no el motor.\"\n            }\n          },\n          {\n            \"text\": \"Angular CLI\",\n            \"correct\": false,\n            \"output\": {\n              \"en\": \"Angular CLI is a tool, not the engine.\",\n              \"es\": \"Angular CLI es una herramienta, no el motor.\"\n            }\n          },\n          {\n            \"text\": \"JavaScript\",\n            \"correct\": false,\n            \"output\": {\n              \"en\": \"JavaScript is the language, not the engine.\",\n              \"es\": \"JavaScript es el lenguaje, no el motor.\"\n            }\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"backgroundColor\": \"#FFF3E0\",\n    \"avatar\": {\n      \"name\": \"Lina\",\n      \"imageUrl\": \"LINK\",\n      \"position\": \"bottomLeft\"\n    }\n  }" },
                                        
